Text.Value: What is the purpose of this tribunal?
*The corpse remains silent. It does not know.*

EditorData.logicalname: DOESN'T KNOW ANSWER - DELETE IF NOT NEEDED

Text.Value: He fell... but that was not the end...

EditorData.InternalNodeContext: This can be generic, not adressing if players kill figaro or if Dolor kills Figaro.

Text.Value: How do you know the Bhaalists are back?
Devella Fountainhead... Constable of... the Flaming Fist...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
He wanted Figaro's hand... for tribunal of Bhaal...
A century ago... a Bhaalspawn ruled... the Iron Throne...
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: This is a SwD dialog for Devella Fountainhead. This SwD dialog will contain information about the bhaal plot and how to go to the Murder Tribunal.
